title: PINK FLOYD 1965 - 2000 ALL SONGS SEPARATE
description:
Please SEED For Others To Enjoy!
Cheers, Bubanee
All studio songs are in order from 1967 to 1994 their numbered
From 006 to 152

1967 The piper at the gates of dawn
1968 A saucerful of secrets
1969 The soundtrack - More
1969 Ummagumma studio and live
1970 Atom heart mother
1971 Meddle
1972 The soundtrack - Obscured by clouds
1973 The dark side of the moon
1975 Wish you were here
1977 Animals
1979 The wall
1982 The final cut
1987 A momentary lapse of reason
1994 The division bell

The 3 Live Albums

1988 Delicate sound of thunder. 153 to 167
1995 Pulse. 168 to 191
2000 1980-81 The Wall. 192 to 221

The 3 Soundtracks

1966 Tonight lets all make love in london. 222 and 223
1970 Zabriskie point. 224 to 230
The Committee. 231 to 239

The Singles and others

The First 5 songs are from the album "Relics"
and the rest from 240 to 253 are made up of
Rare singles and songs, a couple from the album "Works"
You will notice there are songs missing from Relics and Works but they
are just the songs already in the list. i just dont see the point
of having the same song twice! Hope you enjoy the list
